Author: dietingdietdie
Text: Wow, are you me? I slept with a guy I had great chemistry with and I went into it knowing it wasn't going to go anywhere. I thought I could handle it because I \~knew\~ nothing was going to come of it LOL wrong. My appetite has disappeared and I haven't eaten in 2 days.

Author: wondermadness
Text: I’m the same exact way! I stress about my job a lot and so that causes me to not eat or eat very little on the days that I’m working but on my days off I eat like a normal person.
